{"tid":1682761,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"死再多人，被強姦再多，都唔會再令香港人panic","createTime":"2019-10-30T09:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T12:03:25.000Z","uid":101167,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6928eb8c483e1a8dd8249d3c562a1fdc2fb43bba","tid":1682761,"uid":101167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:08:24.000Z","msg":"Nobody panics when things go according to plans<br />\nEven the plan is horrifying<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YEEsE8snXok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYEEsE8snXok&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt3w2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=ac4a9667\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YEEsE8snXok</a><br />\n<br />\n依家死人冧樓，少女被強<br />\n大家都習以為常<br />\n一邊繼續屌黑警<br />\n但一邊覺得黑警咁做唔出奇<br />\n<br />\n呢啲野根本唔會觸碰到香港人既底線<br />\n繼續返工！<br />\n<br />\n呢場鬥爭再拖落去一定唔樂觀<br />\n烏克蘭都識黎個endgame決勝<br />\n點解香港人唔同港府黎個決戰死過？<br />\n仲拖乜？<br />\n<br />\n話我吹風撚又好乜都好<br />\n大家都只係想贏"},{"pid":"797d725002717082bcb2ade17f42feb592be6df2","tid":1682761,"uid":1477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6928eb8c483e1a8dd8249d3c562a1fdc2fb43bba","tid":1682761,"uid":101167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:08:24.000Z","msg":"Nobody panics when things go according to plans<br />\nEven the plan is horrifying<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YEEsE8snXok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYEEsE8snXok&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt3w2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=ac4a9667\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YEEsE8snXok</a><br />\n<br />\n依家死人冧樓，少女被強<br />\n大家都習以為常<br />\n一邊繼續屌黑警<br />\n但一邊覺得黑警咁做唔出奇<br />\n<br />\n呢啲野根本唔會觸碰到香港人既底線<br />\n繼續返工！<br />\n<br />\n呢場鬥爭再拖落去一定唔樂觀<br />\n烏克蘭都識黎個endgame決勝<br />\n點解香港人唔同港府黎個決戰死過？<br />\n仲拖乜？<br />\n<br />\n話我吹風撚又好乜都好<br />\n大家都只係想贏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:36:25.000Z","msg":"其實要達成目標<br />\n不外乎都係開源節流<br />\n開源，好簡單，姐係要令對方加入己方陣營<br />\n都係教育佢地民主是個好東西<br />\n<br />\n但有d 長者唔會明<br />\n咁呢個時候就要節流<b